<plot>Love is Blue is science-fiction, romantic comedy exploring modern perceptions of love. Angus craves someone to love. After many short-term relationships, he wants to find a decent guy and settle down. Luckily for him, cutting edge research is guaranteeing to help people see love. Desperate and used, Angus signs up for the research. He begins to see and experience all kinds of love and lust around him. However, things do not turn out quite as promised. A quirky and heart-felt story that explores modern perceptions of love.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?344587</url></doc>
